{"tid":1434361,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"獵下眼睇左微博幾眼，原來好多大陸人關注香港","createTime":"2019-08-08T18:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T17:40:02.000Z","uid":82224,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e75d37073e8a96e90b174195df5569942d08d91b","tid":1434361,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:04:30.000Z","msg":"有好多唔駛講一味抵毀示威者，粗口漫罵唔駛理<br />\n<br />\n但亦都有有識之士，我地要帶俾大陸一個多角度思考既新思維方式<br />\n<br />\n唔好再咁老土 唔係A就B 非友即敵既 patriotism <br />\n<br />\n有好多大陸人被中共洗腦<br />\n<br />\n我地要發出個訊息，我地唔係反大陸人。我地翻既係免大頭奶粉，地溝油，貪污，官商勾結等不公既事發生係香港；正正香港人需要完全自主先唔會有同等或更甚既獻媚既反送中條例，大白象工程，新移民橫行，官黑勾結，政治審查，警方公權力過大打壓大眾等事而發聲。<br />\n<br />\n香港係好多唔公平事發生，無話佢原本係好好<br />\n<br />\n但我地既動作係保護香港人，make this region can be greater ，免大陸劣等人種入侵.PS我唔可以話文化，sub-culture興起有佢既個人之處，但你話大陸有無好野,有既無可否認，trading 方面。淘寶etc <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">總言之唔好落入中共控制手段！</span>人民鬥人民，香港人鬥大陸人！無資產既鬥有資產，我地要超越一般中共既諗法！"},{"pid":"33511536c5fa4f3d95b157ca67c150900897dedf","tid":1434361,"uid":179402,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:04:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「幫幫手推一推」黑警唔單止搜身時恐嚇市民 仲要強光照市民對眼！ | LIHKG</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF74MRhonX28&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=0aa9b201\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOjM9aG3xZKk&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=06406c59\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有乜野必要同理由對市民使用強光照住佢對眼？呢個行為有咩意義同對工作上有咩幫助？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">強烈要求黑警回應點解要用惡劣 粗暴 令人不適嘅態度 語氣 行為 去對待配合黑警工作嘅市民！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n幫手派出去 推上報<br />\n<br />\n今次拍片者冇事 下個好難講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86528c76cb7383c4c802f5e9bfc9c64fbb1e6f22","tid":1434361,"uid":46748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:05:47.000Z","msg":"推 講得啱"},{"pid":"3d61dc1ec01705c40536e1d1dda91498739835a2","tid":1434361,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:05:51.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"3250d150390f877a913faa2987aa9783fa054091","tid":1434361,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86528c76cb7383c4c802f5e9bfc9c64fbb1e6f22","tid":1434361,"uid":46748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:05:47.000Z","msg":"推 講得啱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:08:55.000Z","msg":"Thx !"},{"pid":"03035764fbda2dd05405c5bab50c01f2d8c5d7ae","tid":1434361,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:10:17.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhhh"},{"pid":"b48f55d7cdcf996bcf1b8eac3c9bcb7744e57dce","tid":1434361,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:12:34.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh"},{"pid":"cb9753c531b82a8145591ef88c6e4a08fba25e70","tid":1434361,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:18:57.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"f90619d15212e1e4a0747468d38554adc4cf2dd9","tid":1434361,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:19:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"09b94ab2fd526097ed68d87614f51662548a3d23","tid":1434361,"uid":294646,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e75d37073e8a96e90b174195df5569942d08d91b","tid":1434361,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,